**TDS on salary** is deducted by employers under Section 192 of the Income Tax Act. The employer estimates your total annual income (salary + other declared income), deducts eligible deductions (under the tax regime chosen), computes the annual tax, divides by 12, and deducts that amount monthly. This calculator replicates this calculation for FY 2026-27.
